+---
+
+## Prior Phase Context
+
+### Phase 3: UI Overhaul ‚Äî Landing Page & Sidebar (COMPLETE)
+
+**A. Deliverables**:
+- `workspace-card.tsx` ‚Äî Server Component, accepts optional `agentSummary` prop (NOT wired)
+- `fleet-status-bar.tsx` ‚Äî Server Component, accepts optional counts (NOT wired, renders null)
+- `worktree-picker.tsx` ‚Äî Client Component, searchable workspace picker
+- `use-attention-title.ts` ‚Äî Hook for browser tab title with ‚ùó prefix (NOT wired in workspace layout)
+- Landing page `page.tsx` ‚Äî Workspace card grid, starred-first, direct DI service calls
+- Sidebar restructured ‚Äî workspace-scoped sections, dev section collapsed
+
+**B. Dependencies Exported**:
+- `WorkspaceCardProps.agentSummary?: { running: number; attention: number }` ‚Äî ready to consume
+- `FleetStatusBarProps: { runningCount?, attentionCount?, firstAttentionHref? }` ‚Äî ready to consume
