+- **useAttentionTitle** (Phase 3): Already implemented ‚Äî just need to call it
+- **Existing tests** (Phase 3): 34 tests for card/fleet/attention ‚Äî they test component rendering, we test data derivation
+- **Toast pattern** (Phase 4 / Plan 042): `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` for settings mutations
