+
+## Deduplication Logic
+
+Recent files must not duplicate working changes:
+
+```typescript
+// In ChangesView:
+const workingPaths = new Set(workingChanges.map(f => f.path));
+const dedupedRecent = recentFiles.filter(f => !workingPaths.has(f));
+```
+
