+## Summary
+
+The browser page composes its layout with raw `div+flex` ‚Äî no reusable panel components exist. This plan creates a three-panel layout system (ExplorerPanel + LeftPanel + MainPanel) in the `_platform/panel-layout` infrastructure domain, adds a git changes view with `git status --porcelain` parsing to the `file-browser` domain, and wires everything into BrowserClient. The result: users can navigate by typing paths, toggle between tree and changes views, and all state is deep-linkable.
